<h1>MY FAVOURITE CHARACTER
    
<h2> Cristiano Ronaldo </h2>    
    
 <p> Ronaldos full name is Cristiano Ronaldo dos Santos Aveiro. Ronaldo is a professional football player. He is a portuguese player, He plays for PORTUGAL in the Fifa World Cup. He plays for JUVENTUS in the Uefa Champions league. He is one of the best players of the world. Ronaldo has won 4 Golden boots

The European Golden shoe, also knwn as European Golden Boot, is an award that is given each season to the leading goalscorer in league matches.
